Interestingly, when rogues were at their worst, I'd mee them and they were the happiest with their class, the ones I meet anyway.<P>I met one and said "ouch, how do you like it", he said he loved it.<P>That's the bottom line... do you like being a summoner, sending your pet to do things for you, etc.? Not crunching numbers who does how much per second, do you like it?<P>Some will, some won't.<P>It's all balance - if they doubled our damage, some would say YAY, now every raid will want tons of mages, you level fast!<P>others would say "bleh, boring now, where's the interesting gameplay, and everyone started a mage."<P>If they halved the damage, some would quit, others would find it more fun to try to get every bit of damage and be less common.
