<IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/profile.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Profile for Tomlyn Drayke"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://" target=_new><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/homepage.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Author's Homepage"></A> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=private_message&u=00003231"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/priv_message.gif" BORDER='0' ALT="Send New Private Message"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=6&t=003847&reply_num=000023&u="><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=6&t=003847&replyto=000023"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Its not about fixing things that are broken...like BO was and like the rains were.  Its about consitently saying we're a dying class blah blah blah.  And if you don't like your new role post 50 why did you play it to 58.  There is a difference between coming in here and saying OMG we suck compared to everyone else...aka whining. And coming on a posting a valid thread about how a spell isn't working as it should and getting feedback from the rest of the mage community.  <BR>There are certain rants I understand..like changing the fire pet post 50, the spell drop situation, and a few others.  But I do get tired of the<BR>1.) We need root, snare, and/or fear, SoW, we are the only casters who don't have...balh blah blah<BR>2.) We need some form of mana regen.  Heck if you want to regen your mana, chain summon 49 pets and reclaim them  <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/smile.gif"> (oops did you speciallize in conjuration like you should have..not like it regens much faster than medding like this anyhow)<BR>3.) "/pet no attack" arguement.  I get tired of that one.  Try "/pet get lost" if you start losing control of your pet. Heck it costs 5 silver to summon another.  They're dumb, protective animals people and we gotta love em for it.<P>I'll fully support a valid question or concern about a broken spell or about blurring of the class lines (like druids getting pets and the monk bracer which has our summons on it...heck, these are the reasons I don't want root/snare/sow/etc..., class blurring gets boring)  I enjoy the uniqueness of me  <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/smile.gif"><P><P>------------------<BR>Tomlyn Drayke<BR>Lvl 49 Mage<BR>Prexus<P>"But whosoever should cross that line, into true corruption,into our domain....One day you will look behind you and you will see We Three, and on that day, YOU WILL REAP IT!" ---"Boondock Saints"
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
